722917f-b.text:
Riverside Park: Three views photographed in a southwestward direction from about 103rd Street. Nos. 2 and 3 show ships at anchor on the Hudson River; several of which are U.S. Navy vessels.
Views 1 & 2:- JJune 7, 1921.
View 3:- June 14, 1921.
Walter L. Bogert.
